text: Inglisella etheridgei is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== The shell grows to a length of 7 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species is found along Victoria (Australia) ==References== * Hemmen J. (2007). Recent Cancellariidae. Wiesbaden, 428pp. ==External links== * Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1880
title: Inglisella etheridgei
